Code Explanation
import socket

Used for basic TCP port scanning. It tries to connect to a target IP and port to check whether the port is open.

import subprocess

Used to run Nmap commands from inside the Python GUI.

import shlex

Used to safely split a custom Nmap command into arguments. This is safer than running raw shell commands.

